description._content: Description: H.M. King Abdullah & his Grandson watching the Arab Aeroplane dropping the pamphlets on the Grounds on Arbor Day in Amman Location: Jordan Date: 15 January 1949 Description: H.M. listening to the opening address delivered by ACF Y Salti on the Arbor Day. Location: Jordan Date: 15 January 1949 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/676 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
